<p>That most recent version was being co-developed by AdHoc Studio - co-founded by the original Wolf <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/games/among-us">Among Us</a> team and now best known as the studio behind last year's stellar Dispatch - but last September it <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/even-the-studio-that-wrote-the-wolf-among-us-2-doesnt-know-whats-going-on-with-it">told Eurogamer it had been off the project for a while</a>.</p><p>The Wolf Among Us 2's Summer Game Fest showing credits Telltale (which was resurrected some years ago now) and publisher PM Studios, with the game now targeting a 2027 release. Before all that, though, there's <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/games/the-wolf-among-us">The Wolf Among Us</a> Remastered, a revamp of the beloved original game, which is set to launch this "holiday".</p>
<p>So there you go - some more good news in what's been an action-packed Summer Game Fest showcase this year. For more on all the big reveals we've seen so far, you can <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/everything-announced-in-summer-game-fest-2026">consult Eurogamer's handy round-up</a>.</p>

